{"tid":2190821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梅西宣布留下，巴賽無人道賀，球王很受傷！僅1人表明態度","createTime":"2020-09-06T04:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T10:40:30.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6bb1d82ee7d2d00422d667fd82476e9d19071f","tid":2190821,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://梅西在接受GOAL.COM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A2%85%E8%A5%BF%E5%9C%A8%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97GOAL.COM&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=f38ca6d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">梅西在接受GOAL.COM</a>採訪時宣布，自己將繼續效力巴薩1年。這場持續了10天的鬧劇，以梅西留下收尾。新賽季的巴薩，梅西還會是隊長嗎？隊友們如何看待梅西？零點電台透露，梅西宣布留下的24小時之內，巴薩沒有人給他傳達支持的信息&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=2msvvru/305164714564676f466c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3D2msvvru%2F305164714564676f466c.jpg&h=7938c4d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n西班牙零點電台著名的足球節目El Transistor中，巴薩記者洛薩諾-尼耶托透露了這樣的消息：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i3.read01.com/SIG=17qv1af/3051647145644e6b4f41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.read01.com%2FSIG%3D17qv1af%2F3051647145644e6b4f41.jpg&h=94b8f3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梅西宣布留下來，不過巴薩的球員中，沒有人發出支持的消息。這讓梅西感到很奇怪，同時也感到很受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/SIG=3qjkadc/3051647145644862694b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2FSIG%3D3qjkadc%2F3051647145644862694b.jpg&h=a121c4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為西班牙正統媒體，零點電台的消息可信度比較高。於情於理，梅西這10天的操作：義無反顧地想離開，炮轟俱樂部，又手撕西甲官方，最後宣布自己「不情不願」地留下，明年自由之身離開，這讓巴薩俱樂部、更衣室很難處理。"},{"pid":"f8363ac5ab873ff42a8acb190e336f325fa25101","tid":2190821,"uid":25345,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"好撚柒<br />\n過街老鼠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8b0936efb60a51f43b5c37caec5192275f3ea2","tid":2190821